{"word":"H142 - אָדַר - ʼâdar - aw-dar' - Glorious - மகிமையான","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>אָדַר"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʼâdar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>aw-dar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Glorious / மகிமையான"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச் சொல்."},{"paragraph":"- மகத்துவமாயிரு, மகிமையுள்ளதாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be great, to be majestic, to be wide, to be noble (poetic)"},{"paragraph":"a) (in the Niphal) to be majestic, to be glorious (as a participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (in the Hiphil) to make glorious"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>expand</i>, that is, <i>be great</i> or (figuratively) <i>magnificent: - </i>(become) glorious, honourable."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H115 - אֲדֹורַיִם - ʼĂdôwrayim - ad-o-rah'-yim/115\">H115</a>, <a href=\"#/H117 - אַדִּיר - ʼaddîyr - ad-deer'/117\">H117</a>, <a href=\"#/H142 - אָדַר - ʼâdar - aw-dar'/142\">H142</a>, <a href=\"#/H143 - אֲדָר - ʼĂdâr - ad-awr'/143\">H143</a>, <a href=\"#/H145 - אֶדֶר - ʼeder - eh'-der/145\">H145</a>, <a href=\"#/H146 - אַדָּר - ʼAddâr - ad-dawr'/146\">H146</a>, <a href=\"#/H152 - אֲדְרַמֶּלֶךְ - ʼĂdrammelek - ad-ram-meh'-lek/152\">H152</a>, <a href=\"#/H155 - אַדֶּרֶת - ʼaddereth - ad-deh'-reth/155\">H155</a>"}]}